<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/e1b42e2a28fe4626a72443d93f9b718a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/183e1527717a45d888c12ba2ef6833f9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>◐他们是专业的 ◐ </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/5006733329c743aaacd6e667f3179dc5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201125/061c7e25b77e4bf4b02dd280824cf5e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">铁板烧、日式烤串...件件都好吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/75912dd5b4d6460dbf48336d5bae73f7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/07f6e00c08a4409d94746e80d1edd074.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/21e8136df8a04760823755d3dbca65ac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>搞啥哦？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ① ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛舌 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/4d52a5fd52b240a6baf72f3b01bf2df4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛舌！<strong>精选的厚切牛舌采用牛舌根部</strong>，属于牛的稀少部位。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 整份桌上现烧 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/2a630abdae954203a19d44bbcaa30efd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/c84048bd3e074441ab7729d49a40d0fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">端上桌由服务生当场“炫技”现烤<strong>，吃起来脆嫩多汁</strong>。表层黄油将其鲜味提了上来，牛香味中带着丝丝鲜甜！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 10cm厚切牛舌 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/bfdfc4df5bcc4803ae6822e5adb6ee83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛舌够厚，不怕会被烤干，调味过的牛舌鲜味更为突出，<strong>入口紧致弹牙，5片就能叠叠叠成10cm高</strong>，厚度感人！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 卷着蒜片生菜一起吃 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/343382617e6c485a84c63ad5448fddfa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/1744ff615a36455f969d7fdcd2ee6b41.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201125/0d7d114a4de54e8cb663b0eb34e8efa3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">配上牛舌旁的蒜片、生菜来吃，<strong>蒜香浸润到爽脆的牛舌里，有点像东北银的吃法，很是过瘾</strong>。沾点盘子边上的芝士酱吃，味道也很nice哦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ② ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一贯金牌鹅肝寿司</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/466728370c5a4cb2a2c62262465f9beb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>入口即化的鹅肝可以说是日料届的宠儿了</strong>，随盘搭配有生姜片，吃完鹅肝以后吃上一点，清新解腻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 现点现烤，肥嫩多汁 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/2fa73dd2f0f94eb1866a02d44544368f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/现点现烧，烤至微微流油/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/0c0782142ef0470aa155d4656432e34e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/涮上秘制酱料于鹅肝表层/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/9245d0491f284c29af27c7edf643c792.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/将大片的鹅肝轻放米饭上/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鹅肝寿司，放进嘴瞬间，<strong>鹅肝粉嫩绵密，加上咸甜适中的酱汁</strong>，醇香浓郁之间，回味无穷！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 厚度堪比iPhone12 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/b5777dcadbd043499dc0aa89488dd4ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不愧为这家店的招牌菜，<strong>鹅肝厚度比iPhone12还厚！</strong>看到这么大块鹅肝盖在饭团上，没烤之前的大小不敢想~吃完忍不住又追加了一份！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ③ ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">海胆酱焗蟹壳烧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/fca626719db04f20bad8559e04af78d3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>以完整蟹壳为底，将蟹肉+金针菇+蔬菜嵌入其中，淋入满满的海胆酱</strong>，面上还撒上了一层蟹籽鱼籽，这是对芝士狂魔的最高礼遇！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/a144d995992647caadfcdd29bded55c3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/768edcad9b084af48f1b815139ad11b8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201125/1343d00fb2f646789a4ec8d24b40d0e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最享受一筷子挖到底的那种幸福感！<strong>破开金黄的外衣，藏了许久的蟹肉和金针菇总算亮相，</strong>一次就能感受到多重口感在口腔里！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ④ ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">串烧拼盘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/0e24c32cc135412e98d8ce9e1876f15a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>六款串烧荤素搭配，一次满足n个愿望简直不要太优秀！</strong>最喜欢是墨鱼肠串串和鸡肉串串，挤上几滴柠檬更多一份清甜~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>「 新鲜烤制，色香味美 」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/d36e9630164a49b2b74a7f296c30174e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/d5bdd6ff329c459babc052630a01cab7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>日料向来以食材新鲜出名</strong>，御前十七的烤串一般只会加些基本调料调味，<strong>外皮烤制得微焦，香嫩适中</strong>，是食客的最爱的味道！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/fb05478ad0aa495b860e9d2dcfd06feb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/1217ea3132234260a1871216a29f0c97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/a5339453cbcf437193d935cad1b62ab2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/df5cdc13a9e14038b5b6e8703dbcb65f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">精美的摆盘就是视觉享受~<strong>烤肥牛、烤五花拼笋、烤云南小瓜、烤墨鱼肠</strong>…6种不同口味的串烧精致诱人，一串接着一串！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/834c18471153445d9660e9bed6440f9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/8e3e2287c05c4876821fa01e4f82db5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/ed495f222a98433bb9b9add28b508be7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/e9a58d11ee2b4d439e59d5390b740bc6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>炙烧黑猪叉烧拉面、沸腾和牛海鲜酸汤、罗勒香蒜焗一口蘑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ① ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">炙烧黑猪叉烧拉面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/8e3e2287c05c4876821fa01e4f82db5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这一款“炙烧黑猪叉烧拉面”，<strong>是老板极力推荐的，也是店里的“王牌拉面”</strong>，端上来就热乎乎的，香味扑鼻，勾得人眼里只能看到它！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/f5abc5be626b4b93ad5e47ebff17c0e6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/8d0d3c61607d4988b41aaac41785440e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>来自伊比利亚的黑毛猪肉，每日手工现卤4h</strong>。经过炙烧后懒洋洋地“瘫”在拉面上，吸尽了拉面的香气，更能吃出满足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/0e3c84b8a2ee45d0a0b8c2804046928f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>//</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/240a6c3277f4412a9f05b81175d0bad8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7cm大块叉烧肉，一大口下去，<strong>嘴里满满都是幼嫩口感与丰沛肉汁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ② ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">沸腾和牛海鲜酸汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/577b2daf42c249729b2abfed7b630b62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>自带4只大虾和澳洲M8和牛的冬阴功酸汤也来了</strong>！上桌沸腾，鲜肉瞬间烫熟，香气扑鼻而来，稍不留神就会让你上瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/99fddb1ffab242979fbf9aea51132af2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/58cc90122cd24e598bc7788aa9221140.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/酸味浓郁，上桌后在石锅中还在沸的“酸、烫、鲜/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鲜虾、香茅、南姜、柠檬叶…10余种配料，<strong>全部选用进口泰式香料，就为了还原纯正的冬阴功滋味！</strong>上桌时石锅还在沸腾，香气扑鼻...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/c298f8ddef464460925c282def41590e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201125/9b3e4b57c0a64fcaa8a316b55edcb599.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201125/30ee9d8713194ca795b8fa3d6177e233.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/d50b93e42e554fb8a81e39963fcb7dc6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>加入大虾、肥牛、白贝的冬阴功鲜甜十足</strong>，一入口就是复杂的泰式香料在舌尖，酸辣的口感，瞬间开胃，<strong>泰料控</strong>爱的就是这口！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· ③ ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">罗勒香蒜焗一口蘑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/1f56b0932b2b48bcad14ca662b94c53c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">经典的罗勒香蒜焗一口蘑，<strong>不仅鲜香美味，而且营养丰富</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/950cceef69ee400bbfbce491e08f9f5d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/f6d139b1662e42afbb3d6d374eca742f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新鲜一口蘑搭配浓浓的罗勒香蒜,大概没有谁会不喜欢，做法简单，<strong>入口质感如肉，软嫩喷香，</strong>一定要记得趁热吃哦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/5ff8b872936f4140a83962e08ac3cdeb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『把日本街景都搬来了 』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>◐ 进店一秒置身日本街头 ◐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201125/377c032eb800479db1440b849c9cda9b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/e883e707f9fb44db8fea14c22e56272d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/673bef66ab0e4dc4bc2336cbfbd41799.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/5e3be8f60d564e19afa23c2e8d038c45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这家藏在番禺的日料屋，还真有让人误入日本街头的感觉，开业以来，“御前十七”凭借<strong>日式风情的环境以及地道的日料美食</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/b8ab35f3ffd24786b1aff8c87de45e0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/a0481ae88fcd498989e8b7bfba83b7df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/7a7060770f9f4f51a7734181b8c0b7e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大气装修，每一处都充满了和风元素。不仅能吃，还能拍照发圈，<strong>多个打卡点设计，一秒出大片！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>◐ 六个独立包厢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/03d405b936134298a676baf9c02cf691.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201125/ab511a51821a4aa1b0a2fde52e6d1e82.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201125/ce965d10025142a09d0bbfb9218b7367.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● Live</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/cfef0f029dc0419da900d1d1681183f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 御前十七 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">📍<strong>店铺地址</strong>:广州市番禺区禺山西路海乐荟广场四楼404-405</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">🕚<strong>营业时间</strong>:11:30-15：30，17:00-21:30</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">🚥<strong>交通指引</strong>:坐地铁3号线B市桥站出口乘坐番16路至海伦堡创意园步行141m</p>
